{"type":"message","id":"5570b9b3","parentId":"3aa4017d","timestamp":"2026-07-10T06:46:00.407Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_024c8ff24fa241e2a2198a54","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndate: 2026-07-10\nn: 1\npillar: Technology & AI innovations\nsource: https://venturebeat.com/orchestration/enterprises-lost-claude-fable-5-for-a-few-weeks-new-data-shows-two-thirds-had-already-built-their-hedge\nsource_date: 2026-07-03\nstatus: pending\n---\n\n𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝗱𝗼𝘄𝗻 𝗹𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗲𝗸. 𝗬𝗼𝘂 𝗱𝗶𝗱𝗻'𝘁 𝗻𝗼𝘁𝗶𝗰𝗲.\n\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\n\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\n\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\n→ Model responds\n→ Agent completes task\n→ Everything works great\n\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\n\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\n\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\n\nIf your monitoring says \"green\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\n\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\n\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783665960403}}
{"type":"message","id":"402f5189","parentId":"5570b9b3","timestamp":"2026-07-10T06:46:17.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_63c8f7fb07c44dacb1979db4","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📝 Post 1/3 — Technology & AI innovations\n\n𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝗱𝗼𝘄𝗻 𝗹𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗲𝗸. 𝗬𝗼𝘂 𝗱𝗶𝗱𝗻'𝘁 𝗻𝗼𝘁𝗶𝗰𝗲.\n\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\n\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\n\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\n→ Model responds\n→ Agent completes task\n→ Everything works great\n\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\n\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\n\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\n\nIf your monitoring says \"green\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\n\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\n\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━\nSource: Claude Fable 5 outage exposed gaps (https://venturebeat.com/orchestration/enterprises-lost-claude-fable-5-for-a-few-weeks-new-data-shows-two-thirds-had-already-built-their-hedge)","presentation":{"blocks":[{"buttons":[{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_approve_2026-07-10-1"},"label":"✅ Publish now","style":"success"},{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_edit_2026-07-10-1"},"label":"✏️ Edit first"},{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_skip_2026-07-10-1"},"label":"⏭️ Skip","style":"secondary"}],"type":"buttons"}]}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"send\", \"message\": \"📝 Post 1/3 — Technology & AI innovations\\n\\n𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝗱𝗼𝘄𝗻 𝗹𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗲𝗸. 𝗬𝗼𝘂 𝗱𝗶𝗱𝗻'𝘁 𝗻𝗼𝘁𝗶𝗰𝗲.\\n\\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\\n\\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\\n\\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\\n→ Model responds\\n→ Agent completes task\\n→ Everything works great\\n\\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\\n\\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\\n\\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\\n\\nIf your monitoring says \\\"green\\\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\\n\\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\\n\\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━\\nSource: Claude Fable 5 outage exposed gaps (https://venturebeat.com/orchestration/enterprises-lost-claude-fable-5-for-a-few-weeks-new-data-shows-two-thirds-had-already-built-their-hedge)\", \"presentation\": {\"blocks\": [{\"buttons\": [{\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_approve_2026-07-10-1\"}, \"label\": \"✅ Publish now\", \"style\": \"success\"}, {\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_edit_2026-07-10-1\"}, \"label\": \"✏️ Edit first\"}, {\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_skip_2026-07-10-1\"}, \"label\": \"⏭️ Skip\", \"style\": \"secondary\"}], \"type\": \"buttons\"}]}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783665960449,"responseId":"KpVQat-KMIyFkuwPt8OP6A4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9b2733a-d697-4e26-a5e1-dc036dd76664","parentId":"402f5189","timestamp":"2026-07-10T06:46:17.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📝 Post 1/3 — Technology & AI innovations\n\n𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝗱𝗼𝘄𝗻 𝗹𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝘄𝗲𝗲𝗸. 𝗬𝗼𝘂 𝗱𝗶𝗱𝗻'𝘁 𝗻𝗼𝘁𝗶𝗰𝗲.\n\nClaude Fable 5 went down for weeks. Only 1 in 10 enterprises had auto-failure detection.\n\nHere's the gap nobody's talking about.\n\nMost teams built their AI stack for happy paths:\n→ Model responds\n→ Agent completes task\n→ Everything works great\n\nBut what happens when the model goes down?\n\nSilent failures. Stuck workflows. Customers waiting. No alerts.\n\nThe enterprises that survived the outage had TWO things:\n1. Multi-model fallback (switch to GPT, Gemini, open-source)\n2. Health checks that actually ping the model — not just the API\n\nIf your monitoring says \"green\" but your agent is frozen, you don't have observability. You have a dashboard.\n\nThe real test: Can you detect a failure BEFORE your customers tell you?\n\nWhen did you last test your AI failure detection?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #Reliability #EnterpriseAI #Monitoring\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━\nSource: Claude Fable 5 outage exposed gaps (https://venturebeat.com/orchestration/enterprises-lost-claude-fable-5-for-a-few-weeks-new-data-shows-two-thirds-had-already-built-their-hedge)"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783665977954,"idempotencyKey":"0f6ec3ff-ebd3-4122-8f90-9929adc471b1:message-tool:vJeZE2aD3gPg5RO8wiHHpL8R:call_63c8f7fb07c44dacb1979db4"}}
