{"type":"message","id":"eeeac723","parentId":"a1deda46","timestamp":"2026-07-10T06:46:59.153Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_64912f42ad3a4dcc8b9511bb","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📝 Post 3/3 — Technology & AI innovations\n\n𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗯𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗯𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴. 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗲'𝘀 𝘄𝗵𝘆.\n\nEveryone's chasing the most autonomous, most intelligent, most powerful AI agent.\n\nBut the teams shipping real value? They're doing the opposite.\n\nThey're building BORING agents:\n→ One clear task\n→ Defined success criteria\n→ Human in the loop for edge cases\n→ Fails gracefully, not spectacularly\n\nBoring means predictable. Predictable means trustworthy. Trustworthy means adoption.\n\nThe flashiest AI demo you saw last week? Probably broken in production.\n\nThe boring agent that just works? That's the one getting renewed.\n\nStop optimizing for impressive. Start optimizing for reliable.\n\nWhat's the most boring AI agent you could ship this week?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #EnterpriseAI #SoftwareEngineering #Reliability\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━\nSource: Original insight — benchmark-first development philosophy","presentation":{"blocks":[{"buttons":[{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_approve_2026-07-10-3"},"label":"✅ Publish now","style":"success"},{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_edit_2026-07-10-3"},"label":"✏️ Edit first"},{"action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_skip_2026-07-10-3"},"label":"⏭️ Skip","style":"secondary"}],"type":"buttons"}]}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"send\", \"message\": \"📝 Post 3/3 — Technology & AI innovations\\n\\n𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗯𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗯𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴. 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗲'𝘀 𝘄𝗵𝘆.\\n\\nEveryone's chasing the most autonomous, most intelligent, most powerful AI agent.\\n\\nBut the teams shipping real value? They're doing the opposite.\\n\\nThey're building BORING agents:\\n→ One clear task\\n→ Defined success criteria\\n→ Human in the loop for edge cases\\n→ Fails gracefully, not spectacularly\\n\\nBoring means predictable. Predictable means trustworthy. Trustworthy means adoption.\\n\\nThe flashiest AI demo you saw last week? Probably broken in production.\\n\\nThe boring agent that just works? That's the one getting renewed.\\n\\nStop optimizing for impressive. Start optimizing for reliable.\\n\\nWhat's the most boring AI agent you could ship this week?\\n\\n#AI #AIAgents #EnterpriseAI #SoftwareEngineering #Reliability\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━\\nSource: Original insight — benchmark-first development philosophy\", \"presentation\": {\"blocks\": [{\"buttons\": [{\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_approve_2026-07-10-3\"}, \"label\": \"✅ Publish now\", \"style\": \"success\"}, {\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_edit_2026-07-10-3\"}, \"label\": \"✏️ Edit first\"}, {\"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_skip_2026-07-10-3\"}, \"label\": \"⏭️ Skip\", \"style\": \"secondary\"}], \"type\": \"buttons\"}]}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783666005424,"responseId":"V5VQaoSQIKvx3PQPgd-yiAo"}}
{"type":"message","id":"524a73fa-bd24-4b1e-8464-fddedf687044","parentId":"eeeac723","timestamp":"2026-07-10T06:46:59.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📝 Post 3/3 — Technology & AI innovations\n\n𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗯𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝗔𝗜 𝗮𝗴𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗯𝗼𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴. 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗲'𝘀 𝘄𝗵𝘆.\n\nEveryone's chasing the most autonomous, most intelligent, most powerful AI agent.\n\nBut the teams shipping real value? They're doing the opposite.\n\nThey're building BORING agents:\n→ One clear task\n→ Defined success criteria\n→ Human in the loop for edge cases\n→ Fails gracefully, not spectacularly\n\nBoring means predictable. Predictable means trustworthy. Trustworthy means adoption.\n\nThe flashiest AI demo you saw last week? Probably broken in production.\n\nThe boring agent that just works? That's the one getting renewed.\n\nStop optimizing for impressive. Start optimizing for reliable.\n\nWhat's the most boring AI agent you could ship this week?\n\n#AI #AIAgents #EnterpriseAI #SoftwareEngineering #Reliability\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━\nSource: Original insight — benchmark-first development philosophy"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783666019369,"idempotencyKey":"0f6ec3ff-ebd3-4122-8f90-9929adc471b1:message-tool:HtQmm8k4hXjAHdWf97Il8HQ1:call_64912f42ad3a4dcc8b9511bb"}}
